column5: Note: Checkin on Saturday, June 24 is 5:30 pm and not a minute earlier. Please only book this Saturday night if you are okay with that time.  3 miles from Downtown, 1.8 miles from Soco District -Private space, Sleeps 2 on a new memory foam mattress -24-hour check-in - Fiber WIFI, Air conditioning, Kitchenette -Share living area, kitchen, bathroom, and shower in house -Allergy free - no pets, ever
